OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fthis evening with winds easing, then
OL,7,Fdry and mostly fine overnight. Chance
OL,8,Fof a few localised mist or fog patches
OL,9,Fdeveloping inland late in the night
OL,10,Fand becoming rather chilly by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FGenerally dry with plenty of
OL,13,Fhazy sunshine through the morning.
OL,14,FCloud increasing from the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith a risk of showers, perhaps
OL,16,Fturning thundery by the evening. Light
OL,17,For gentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
