OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright for much of Tuesday and
OL,7,FThursday with sunny spells. Cloudier
OL,8,Fon Wednesday with some early rain
OL,9,Flikely. Warm Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,10,Fperhaps locally very warm by Thursday.
